\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<h3 class=\\\"widget-title\\\">TOM I D\\u017dERI<\\/h3><div class=\\\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\\\"><p class=\\\"card-text\\\">Kloi Grejs Morec nalazi se u ulozi tek zaposlene Kajle, koja ima zadatak da re\\u0161i problem glodavaca u hotelu pre va\\u017enog doga\\u0111aja. Kajla za pomo\\u0107 uzima Toma kako bi zajedni\\u010dki zaustavili nesta\\u0161nog D\\u017eerija. Sledi naravno epska bitka ma\\u010dke i mi\\u0161a koja preti da uni\\u0161ti njenu karijeru, ven\\u010danje, a mogu\\u0107e i ugled samog hotela. No, uskoro se pojavljuje jo\\u0161 ve\\u0107i problem: zlobni i ambiciozni zaposleni koji se urotio protiv njih troje.<\\/p><\\/div>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":true}],\"isInner\":true}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"63aae3f\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"2b7b350\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"bcba1fe\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"spacer\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"3e4d595\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"background_background\":\"classic\",\"background_color\":\"#000000\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"88b78a1\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"d7870ac\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"structure\":\"20\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"b7dfdfd\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"3c373de\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/Nikolaiss7119\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2021\\/05\\/unnamed.jpg\",\"id\":368},\"image_size\":\"medium\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":true},{\"id\":\"780aa83\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"c7df410\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<h3 class=\\\"widget-title\\\">DU\\u0160A<\\/h3><div class=\\\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\\\"><p class=\\\"card-text\\\">U 2020. godini Pixar Animation Studios vodi nas na putovanje od ulica Njujorka do kosmi\\u010dkih kraljevstava, kako bismo otkrili odgovore na najva\\u017enija pitanja u \\u017eivotu. U re\\u017eiji dvostrukog dobitnika oskara, Pita Doktera (\\u201cDo neba\\u201d, \\u201cU mojoj glavi\\u201d).<\\/p><\\/div>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":true}],\"isInner\":true}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"d93346a\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"f67266d\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"79ca74a\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"spacer\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"28e7df4\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"background_background\":\"classic\",\"background_color\":\"#000000\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"2b06aef\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"63dc92c\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"structure\":\"20\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"fb13d56\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"70a9cd7\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/Nikolaiss7119\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2021\\/05\\/bezrepi-peel.jpg\",\"id\":369},\"image_size\":\"medium\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":true},{\"id\":\"379f215\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"4ddd698\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<h3 class=\\\"widget-title\\\">BEZREPI PELE<\\/h3><div class=\\\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\\\"><p class=\\\"card-title\\\">Jedna dan iznenadna oluja povede ovo simpati\\u010dno bezrepo ma\\u010de u pravu avanturu u jedan \\u010dudan grad. Tamo Pele upoznaje nove drugare i razvija veliko prijatljstvo. Me\\u0111utim, nije uvek lako biti nova ma\\u010dka u gradu. Nemaju svi dobre namere i ubrzo Pele silno \\u017eeli da se vrati kuc\\u0301i.<\\/p><\\/div>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":true}],\"isInner\":true}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"3d740e2\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"7259185\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"2d61ccc\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"spacer\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"124e189\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"background_background\":\"classic\",\"background_color\":\"#070707\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"a503e53\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"61889fa\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"structure\":\"20\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"613bed4\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"50a0a2a\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/Nikolaiss7119\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2021\\/05\\/CROODS.jpg\",\"id\":370},\"image_size\":\"medium\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":true},{\"id\":\"65f5aac\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"72f88e8\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<h3 class=\\\"widget-title\\\">KRUDS - NOVO DOBA<\\/h3><div class=\\\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\\\"><p class=\\\"card-text\\\">Ova komedija, nominovana za Oskara, je pri\\u010da o suo\\u010davanju jednog klana sa svojim svetom koji se menja. Bio je to vanvremenski podsetnik na va\\u017enost porodice i na to koliko smo malo evoluirali. Opet su tu zvezde, Nikolas Kejd\\u017e, Ema Stoun, Rajan Rejnolds, Ketrin Kinir, Klark Djuk, uz Lesli Man i Pitera Dinklid\\u017ea koji se pridru\\u017euju porodici Kruds, kako bi se suo\\u010dili s najve\\u0107om pretnjom otkad su napustili pe\\u0107inu, a to je druga porodica.<\\/p><\\/div>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":true}],\"isInner\":true}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
