 class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n	<p class=\"card-text\">Dok eka svoj let na aerodromu u Parizu, uspenom arhitekti Deremiju prilazi jedna krajnje neobina i brbljiva devojka. Zbog njenog nasrtljivog ponaanja, Deremi gubi let, a dok eka sledei avion, nikako ne uspeva da se otarasi dosadne neznanke. Iako se njihov susret ini sluajnim, uskoro e doi do zaokreta koji e njegov znaaj transformisati u neto mnogo opasnije.</p>\n<p class=\"card-text\">\n</p><p><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-352\" src=\"http://localhost/Nikolaiss7119/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/perfect-enemy-212x300.jpg\" alt=\"perfect enemy\" width=\"212\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<p><small class=\"text-muted\">U bioskopima!</small></p>\n</div>\n</div></div></div><div id=\"panel-347-0-0-2\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-last-child\" data-index=\"2\" data-style=\"{&quot;padding&quot;:&quot;4px 4px 4px 4px&quot;,&quot;background&quot;:&quot;#000000&quot;,&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;margin&quot;:&quot;5px 5px 5px 5px&quot;}\" ><div class=\"panel-widget-style panel-widget-style-for-347-0-0-2\" ><div class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\"><h3 class=\"widget-title\">TOM I DERI </h3>\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n	<p class=\"card-text\">Kloi Grejs Morec nalazi se u ulozi tek zaposlene Kajle, koja ima zadatak da rei problem glodavaca u hotelu pre vanog dogaaja. Kajla za pomo uzima Toma kako bi zajedniki zaustavili nestanog Derija. Sledi naravno epska bitka make i mia koja preti da uniti njenu karijeru, venanje, a mogue i ugled samog hotela. No, uskoro se pojavljuje jo vei problem: zlobni i ambiciozni zaposleni koji se urotio protiv njih troje.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-367\" src=\"http://localhost/Nikolaiss7119/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/slika5-240x300.jpg\" alt=\"slika5\" width=\"240\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<p><small class=\"text-muted\">U bioskopima!</small></p>\n</div>\n</div></div></div></div><div id=\"pgc-347-0-1\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\"  data-weight=\"0.25\" ><div id=\"panel-347-0-1-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-first-child\" data-index=\"3\" data-style=\"{&quot;padding&quot;:&quot;4px 4px 4px 4px&quot;,&quot;background&quot;:&quot;#000000&quot;,&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;margin&quot;:&quot;5px 5px 5px 5px&quot;}\" ><div class=\"panel-widget-style panel-widget-style-for-347-0-1-0\" ><div class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\"><h3 class=\"widget-title\">SEANJA IZ ITALIJE </h3>\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n	<p>Boemski umetnik putuje iz Londona u Italiju kako bi prodao kuu koju je nasledio od pokojne supruge. Drutvo mu pravi otueni sin, a putovanje e biti idealno vreme da porade na svom porodinom odnosu.</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-358 size-medium\" src=\"http://localhost/Nikolaiss7119/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/made-it-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"made it\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<p>U bioskopima!</p>\n</div>\n</div></div></div><div id=\"panel-347-0-1-1\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor\" data-index=\"4\" data-style=\"{&quot;padding&quot;:&quot;4px 4px 4px 4px&quot;,&quot;background&quot;:&quot;#000000&quot;,&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;margin&quot;:&quot;5px 5px 5px 5px&quot;}\" ><div class=\"panel-widget-style panel-widget-style-for-347-0-1-1\" ><div class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\"><h3 class=\"widget-title\">GODZILA PROTIV KONGA</h3>\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n	<p class=\"card-text\">Svet je spreman za jo jednu borbu giganta. Kralj udovita i kralj Ostrva lobanja kreu jedan na drugog u borbi za nadmonu monstruoznu superiornost. Dve najmonije sile prirode na planeti sukobljavaju se u najspektakularnijoj bici svih vremena.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-355\" src=\"http://localhost/Nikolaiss7119/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/slika2-galerija-202x300.jpg\" alt=\"godyila\" width=\"202\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<p>U bioskopima!</p>\n</div>\n</div></div></div><div id=\"panel-347-0-1-2\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-last-child\" data-index=\"5\" data-style=\"{&quot;padding&quot;:&quot;4px 4px 4px 4px&quot;,&quot;background&quot;:&quot;#000000&quot;,&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;margin&quot;:&quot;5px 5px 5px 5px&quot;}\" ><div class=\"panel-widget-style panel-widget-style-for-347-0-1-2\" ><div class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\"><h3 class=\"widget-title\">DUA</h3>\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n	<p class=\"card-text\">U 2020. godini Pixar Animation Studios vodi nas na putovanje od ulica Njujorka do kosmikih kraljevstava, kako bismo otkrili odgovore na najvanija pitanja u ivotu. U reiji dvostrukog dobitnika oskara, Pita Doktera (Do neba, U mojoj glavi).</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-368\" src=\"http://localhost/Nikolaiss7119/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/unnamed-203x300.jpg\" alt=\"dusa\" width=\"203\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<p>U bioskopima!</p>\n</div>\n</div></div></div></div><div id=\"pgc-347-0-2\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\"  data-weight=\"0.25\" ><div id=\"panel-347-0-2-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-first-child\" data-index=\"6\" data-style=\"{&quot;padding&quot;:&quot;4px 4px 4px 4px&quot;,&quot;background&quot;:&quot;#000000&quot;,&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;margin&quot;:&quot;5px 5px 5px 5px&quot;}\" ><div class=\"panel-widget-style panel-widget-style-for-347-0-2-0\" ><div class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\"><h3 class=\"widget-title\">RAJA I POSLEDNJI ZMAJ</h3>\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n	<p>Davno, u arobnom gradu Kumandra, ljudi i zmajevi iveli su zajedno u slozi. Ali kada su zlokobna udovita poznata kao Drun postala pretnja za planetu, zmajevi su rtvujui sebe, spasli oveanstvo. Sada, 500 godina kasnije, ta ista udovita su se vratila. Usamljena ratnica Raja mora da ue u trag poslednjem zmaju u nadi da e zauvek da zaustavi neprijatelja. Meutim, tokom svog putovanja nauie da je za spas sveta potrebno neto vie od magije  neophodno je i poverenje.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-363\" src=\"http://localhost/Nikolaiss7119/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/raja-210x300.jpg\" alt=\"raja\" width=\"210\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<p>U bioskopima!</p>\n</div>\n</div></div></div><div id=\"panel-347-0-2-1\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor\" data-index=\"7\" data-style=\"{&quot;padding&quot;:&quot;4px 4px 4px 4px&quot;,&quot;background&quot;:&quot;#000000&quot;,&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;margin&quot;:&quot;5px 5px 5px 5px&quot;}\" ><div class=\"panel-widget-style panel-widget-style-for-347-0-2-1\" ><div class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\"><h3 class=\"widget-title\">ZDRAVICA</h3>\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n	<p class=\"card-text\">Zaglavljen na porodinom okupljanju zbog kojeg eli da izludi, Adrian eka. eka da Sonja odgovori na njegovu SMS poruku i okona pauzu na kojoj su ve mesec dana. Ba tada dobija poziv da odri zdravicu povodom sestrinog venanja. Adrian panii, ali ta ako je ova zdravica neto najbolje to mu se moglo dogoditi?</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-364\" src=\"http://localhost/Nikolaiss7119/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/komedija1-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"komedija1\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<p>U bioskopima!</p>\n</div>\n</div></div></div><div id=\"panel-347-0-2-2\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-last-child\" data-index=\"8\" data-style=\"{&quot;padding&quot;:&quot;4px 4px 4px 4px&quot;,&quot;background&quot;:&quot;#000000&quot;,&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;margin&quot;:&quot;5px 5px 5px 5px&quot;}\" ><div class=\"panel-widget-style panel-widget-style-for-347-0-2-2\" ><div class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\"><h3 class=\"widget-title\">BEZREPI PELE</h3>\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n	<p class=\"card-title\">Jedna dan iznenadna oluja povede ovo simpatino bezrepo mae u pravu avanturu u jedan udan grad. Tamo Pele upoznaje nove drugare i razvija veliko prijatljstvo. Meutim, nije uvek lako biti nova maka u gradu. Nemaju svi dobre namere i ubrzo Pele silno eli da se vrati kuci.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-369\" src=\"http://localhost/Nikolaiss7119/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/bezrepi-peel-212x300.jpg\" alt=\"bezrepi peel\" width=\"212\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<p><small class=\"text-muted\">Vie nije dostupno!</small></p>\n</div>\n</div></div></div></div><div id=\"pgc-347-0-3\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\"  data-weight=\"0.25\" ><div id=\"panel-347-0-3-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-first-child\" data-index=\"9\" data-style=\"{&quot;padding&quot;:&quot;4px 4px 4px 4px&quot;,&quot;background&quot;:&quot;#000000&quot;,&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;margin&quot;:&quot;5px 5px 5px 5px&quot;}\" ><div class=\"panel-widget-style panel-widget-style-for-347-0-3-0\" ><div class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\"><h3 class=\"widget-title\">DUBLERKA</h3>\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n	<p class=\"card-text\">Ne vie tako aktuelna glumica Kendi (Dru Barimor), uhvaena zbog utaje poreza, angauje svoju bivu dublerku Paulu (takoe Dru Barimor) da ide na rehabilitaciju umesto nje. Izmeu njih se razvija specifian odnos kada Kendi shvati da moe da koristiti Paulu kao rezervnu ulogu za sve stresne delove svog ivota. Ali Paula u potpunosti prihvata svoj novi identitet, preuzimajuci Kendinu karijeru i deka, da bi na kraju izbacila Kendi iz sopstvene kuce! Kendi sada mora da preivi u stvarnom svetu dok se Paula grevito dri krhkog, ali slavnog ivota o kojem je oduvek sanjala.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-365\" src=\"http://localhost/Nikolaiss7119/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/stad-203x300.jpg\" alt=\"stad\" width=\"203\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<p><small class=\"text-muted\">Vie nije dostupno!</small></p>\n</div>\n</div></div></div><div id=\"panel-347-0-3-1\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor\" data-index=\"10\" data-style=\"{&quot;padding&quot;:&quot;4px 4px 4px 4px&quot;,&quot;background&quot;:&quot;#000000&quot;,&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;margin&quot;:&quot;5px 5px 5px 5px&quot;}\" ><div class=\"panel-widget-style panel-widget-style-for-347-0-3-1\" ><div class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\"><h3 class=\"widget-title\">KLOPA, PIE I DRUGARI</h3>\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n	<p>Ebi se raduje oputenom Danu zahvalnosti sa najboljom prijateljicom Moli. Ali planovi prijateljica za tihu veeru uz curetinu nestaju kad im se pridrue Molin novi deko i njena ekscentrina majka. Smestite tu i upadae na urku, ukljuujuci Molinu staru ljubav, amana u pokuaju i trio gej vile zatitnice, i eto recepta za komino haotian odmor koji niko nikada nece zaboraviti - ak i da je eleo!</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-366\" src=\"http://localhost/Nikolaiss7119/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Friendsgiving-203x300.jpg\" alt=\"Friendsgiving\" width=\"203\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<p>U bioskopima!</p>\n</div>\n</div></div></div><div id=\"panel-347-0-3-2\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-last-child\" data-index=\"11\" data-style=\"{&quot;padding&quot;:&quot;4px 4px 4px 4px&quot;,&quot;background&quot;:&quot;#000000&quot;,&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;margin&quot;:&quot;5px 5px 5px 5px&quot;}\" ><div class=\"panel-widget-style panel-widget-style-for-347-0-3-2\" ><div class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\"><h3 class=\"widget-title\">KRUDS - NOVO DOBA</h3>\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n	<p class=\"card-text\">Ova komedija, nominovana za Oskara, je pria o suoavanju jednog klana sa svojim svetom koji se menja. Bio je to vanvremenski podsetnik na vanost porodice i na to koliko smo malo evoluirali. Opet su tu zvezde, Nikolas Kejd, Ema Stoun, Rajan Rejnolds, Ketrin Kinir, Klark Djuk, uz Lesli Man i Pitera Dinklida koji se pridruuju porodici Kruds, kako bi se suoili s najveom pretnjom otkad su napustili peinu, a to je druga porodica.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-370\" src=\"http://localhost/Nikolaiss7119/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/CROODS-203x300.jpg\" alt=\"CROODS\" width=\"203\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<p><small class=\"text-muted\">Uskoro, od 27.05 poetak prikazivanja!</small></p>\n</div>\n</div></div></div></div></div></div>', 'Filmovi', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '347-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-05-21 23:40:44', '2021-05-21 23:40:44', '', 347, 'http://localhost/Nikolaiss7119/?p=371', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
